---
import "../styles/global.css"
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
---

<html lang="en" class="bg-[#141414] text-white font-['Fira_Code']">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
    <title>Projects | KyfStore11k</title>
    <meta name="description" content="Explore projects by KyfStore11k on itch.io and GitHub." />
    <link rel="icon" href="/favicon.svg" />
</head>
<body class="min-h-screen p-6 relative">
<Header />

<main class="max-w-4xl mx-auto mt-24 p-6 bg-[#1e1e1e] rounded-lg shadow-lg backdrop-blur-md border border-red-700">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-red-500 mb-6 drop-shadow-lg">My Projects</h1>

    <p class="text-gray-300 mb-6 leading-relaxed">
        Here you can check out my latest game projects and coding work. I’m constantly building and sharing new stuff, so keep an eye on these pages!
    </p>

    <div class="space-y-6">
        <section>
            <h2 class="text-red-400 font-semibold text-2xl mb-3">Games & Demos (itch.io)</h2>
            <p class="text-gray-300 mb-3">
                Explore my game creations, prototypes, and demos available on itch.io. Feel free to try them out and give feedback!
            </p>
            <a
                    href="https://kyfstore.itch.io"
                    target="_blank"
                    rel="noopener noreferrer"
                    class="inline-block px-5 py-3 bg-red-600 rounded-lg shadow-md hover:bg-red-700 transition transform hover:scale-105"
            >
                Visit my itch.io
            </a>
        </section>

        <section>
            <h2 class="text-red-400 font-semibold text-2xl mb-3">Code & Projects (GitHub)</h2>
            <p class="text-gray-300 mb-3">
                Browse my repositories on GitHub where I share source code, libraries, and tools for game development and programming.
            </p>
            <a
                    href="https://github.com/KyfStore11k"
                    target="_blank"
                    rel="noopener noreferrer"
                    class="inline-block px-5 py-3 bg-red-600 rounded-lg shadow-md hover:bg-red-700 transition transform hover:scale-105"
            >
                Visit my GitHub
            </a>
        </section>
    </div>

    <a href="/" class="inline-block mt-8 text-red-600 font-semibold hover:text-red-400 transition underline">
        ← Back to Home
    </a>
</main>

<div class="fixed bottom-10 right-10 w-48 h-48 bg-gradient-to-tr from-red-700 via-pink-600 to-purple-700 opacity-20 rounded-full blur-3xl animate-pulse -z-10"></div>
</body>
</html>
